          <h3>
           <a href="https://quadblog.stanford.edu/2019/03/07/in-support-of-our-community/">
            In support of our community
           </a>
          </h3>
          <div class="row">
           <div class="post-attribution col-md-5 ">
            <div class="author-avatar">
             <img alt="" class="avatar avatar-60 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-60 photo avatar-default" height="60" src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/40c7da9356832a9d5b561ee04a5ed6eb?s=60&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g" width="60"/>
            </div>
            <div class="author-name">
             <a href="https://quadblog.stanford.edu/author/president/" rel="author" title="Posts by Marc Tessier-Lavigne">
              Marc Tessier-Lavigne
             </a>
             <br/>
             <span class="author-title">
              President
             </span>
            </div>
           </div>
           <div class="post-attribution col-md-5 ">
            <div class="author-avatar">
             <img alt="Persis Drell" class="avatar avatar-60 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-60 alignnone photo" height="60" src="https://quadblog.stanford.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/12/2017/09/provost-gravatar-sm.jpg" width="60"/>
            </div>
            <div class="author-name">
             <a href="https://quadblog.stanford.edu/author/provost/" rel="author" title="Posts by Persis Drell">
              Persis Drell
             </a>
             <br/>
             <span class="author-title">
              Provost
             </span>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          As our country works to both advance innovation and protect national security, let us also make sure to reject prejudice and discrimination in all their forms.
          <p>
           <a class="post-link" href="https://quadblog.stanford.edu/2019/03/07/in-support-of-our-community/">
            Read the post »
           </a>
          </p>
         </div>
